{"tid":405530,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8plus要玩快充點做最好","createTime":"2017-09-19T02:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T02:46:05.000Z","uid":5793,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9a673c37f95dc483b75b62ab92af8bae535a55","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"諗緊2個方法<br />\n1.另買佢個無線充電座(7.5W)  價值$498<br />\n2.另買個29W USB-C火牛+Lightning至USB-C線 價值$388+188=$576 (Qi標準快速充電)<br />\n<br />\n屌咁其實Apple食你呢啲配件錢仲爽過賺你買機錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想玩佢個快充呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b39c918e1097d79fe68b349360eb777085e0135","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"其實個無線充電座都係多原裝1A頭5W多2.5W <br />\n其實好似差別不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fa7e4f6b2fe9d40d96db0d8bf0f97f11e040c8","tid":405530,"uid":7109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"用線"},{"pid":"17dd7155c47254edc37e90e45981a560bc866838","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用線</blockquote><br />\n即係option 2?"},{"pid":"3792127a9bb13f201684b65c3cc401da23be2c99","tid":405530,"uid":15970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlightning"},{"pid":"1276af4ce6efe3b1ea4d07163a330b8884b115a3","tid":405530,"uid":40672,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:30:52.000Z","msg":"買note8"},{"pid":"275491ce84834aeef624d3f9e43ddbcf81bfa3c5","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買note8</blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2b134c95f141b5e4