 />\n用圖答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n官網cap</blockquote><br />\n快充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =中學同學&gt;中同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲真係好柒 今晚約左中同八半啊<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓上屌緊叉同充 唔係縮寫"},{"pid":"7291e0ea11e8bbcd6c4ec8e421a53c70302708da","tid":405530,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初初見流出消息以為佢會直接跟lighting - type-c線俾你快叉<br />\n點知apple連呢啲都要賺到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有咩An機係跟埋QC charger？</blockquote><br />\n用過部部都跟<br />\n淘隻都係十零蚊，點會唔跟比你</blockquote><br />\n你嘅QC指5V2A定Qualcomm個隻<br />\nQualcomm個隻我買過兩次Sony都無"},{"pid":"8d7c0f99d2e57c766cfa07baecaacfec68351993","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>快你老母個充<br />\n<br />\n快叉呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/135455_5879a0de52c7ff95e6faed1d82dc44dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F135455_5879a0de52c7ff95e6faed1d82dc44dd.jpg&h=edd3b18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用圖答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n官網cap</blockquote><br />\n快充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =中學同學&gt;中同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw平時唔會講中同呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab49d20f801194c98223086baa1c54eaf65033","tid":405530,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初初見流出消息以為佢會直接跟lighting - type-c線俾你快叉<br />\n點知apple連呢啲都要賺到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有咩An機係跟埋QC charger？</blockquote><br />\n用過部部都跟<br />\n淘隻都係十零蚊，點會唔跟比你</blockquote><br />\n你嘅QC指5V2A定Qualcomm個隻<br />\nQualcomm個隻我買過兩次Sony都無</blockquote><br />\n其實QC是咪頭半個鍾好快之後就慢慢黎<br />\n平時屋企用緊2.1A頭叉電係快過原裝1A頭好多<br />\n即係QC&gt;2.1A&gt;1A咁？"},{"pid":"a6e0035813a73e33a98c04f1bc09d39d2787a406","tid":405530,"uid":42469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初初見流出消息以為佢會直接跟lighting - type-c線俾你快叉<br />\n點知apple連呢啲都要賺到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有咩An機係跟埋QC charger？</blockquote><br />\n用過部部都跟<br />\n淘隻都係十零蚊，點會唔跟比你</blockquote><br />\n你嘅QC指5V2A定Qualcomm個隻<br />\nQualcomm個隻我買過兩次Sony都無</blockquote><br />\n其實QC是咪頭半個鍾好快之後就慢慢黎<br />\n平時屋企用緊2.1A頭叉電係快過原裝1A頭好多<br />\n即係QC&gt;2.1A&gt;1A咁？</blockquote><br />\n所有叉電都係先快後慢<br />\nQC&gt;2.1A&gt;1A無錯，不過iPhone無QC<br />\nQC係Qualcomm專利，我唔知新iPhone個快叉點設計，不過我諗都慢過QC"},{"pid":"cce3fb32011dbaffd1f281b3635cb366cb6a6f96","tid":405530,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初初見流出消息以為佢會直接跟lighting - type-c線俾你快叉<br />\n點知apple連呢啲都要賺到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有咩An機係跟埋QC charger？</blockquote><br />\n用過部部都跟<br />\n淘隻都係十零蚊，點會唔跟比你</blockquote><br />\n你嘅QC指5V2A定Qualcomm個隻<br />\nQualcomm個隻我買過兩次Sony都無</blockquote><br />\nLG, Samsung都有跟QC牛<br />\nOneplus有跟Dash牛，Oneplus/OPPO雖然係Qualcomm但唔行QC，行自家Dash 5V4A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}